            Rubicon Infrastructure Advisors        

            Cork Institute of Technology, Bishopstown, Cork, Ireland        

Jobs

    Follow











                Rubicon's team members are internationally recognised as market leaders in advisory and financial services within the infrastructure sector. The collective team has over 100 years of infrastructure and banking experience and have advised or structured over $90 billion of financing in multiple areas within the infrastructure market.            







            More about us        


        These areas of the infrastructure market include leading global infrastructure sponsors and investors, including social infrastructure (healthcare, education, public buildings), transportation (roads, rail, seaports, airports), energy (generation, transmission, distribution), environmental (water, waste) and renewables (wind, solar).    





            Key competencies and accomplishments of the team        


        Extensive global experience in all key areas of infrastructure
Proven delivery of innovative solutions within the infrastructure sector
Proven track record (team members have won over 30 national and global infrastructure awards)
Significant experience as principal equity investor and project finance lender
Comprehensive infrastructure cash-flow modelling capabilities
Extensive structuring and restructuring experience
Diverse language skills
Strong relationships with key infrastructure players
Established track record in sourcing and structuring transactions
Extensive experience in coordinating and managing the sell-side and buy-side procurement process
Broad understanding of client needs and the ability to deliver a wide scope of services
Diverse backgrounds providing various perspectives and points of view    





            Our Principles        


        Rubicon is built on a strong set of principles which guide its activities and operations.
CREATIVITY: Rubicon fosters a culture of creativity; a value reflected in our work. We constantly challenge ourselves to think outside the box and to design creative solutions for our clients' needs.
INNOVATION: Rubicon prides itself on its innovative thinking and problem solving approach. In rapidly changing markets, there is a need to come up with new ideas and original methods to structure deals and transactions to maximise results for clients. Rubicon strives to be to the fore of market Innovation. We are not merely happy to follow the lead of others; we wish to create innovative processes and structures that blaze trails for the market to follow.
RESULTS: We are results driven at Rubicon. All our work is undertaken with an end goal in mind. Our dedicated team will ensure that a positive outcome is achieved for our clients.
CLIENT FOCUS: At Rubicon we understand the importance of our clients - we ensure they are at the epicentre of everything we do. Our products are carefully crafted to the individual needs of a specific client.
RELATIONSHIPS: The creation and maintenance of good working relationships is integral to Rubicon's success. We strive to ensure that we treat all people with dignity and respect in all our dealings.
PEOPLE: At Rubicon, we understand that our greatest asset is our people. It is our people that will deliver outstanding service and results to our clients. In order to ensure world-class service, we hire the very best people to work for us. We believe in nurturing talent and providing a working environment that is conducive to ensuring the long-term retention of such talent.
LIFE-LONG LEARNING: We are not happy to be merely content with the knowledge and skills we currently have. Just as the business world never stops developing, neither should our learning. The firm's culture is to promote continued learning. Rubicon believes in organising various workshops and other training activities to ensure our employees are constantly improving their skills.
INTEGRITY: Integrity plays a key role in Rubicon's activities. We promise to act honestly and fairly in all operations we engage in. We guarantee to provide impartial and objective advice that is best served to meet our client's needs and not our own.
CONFIDENTIALITY: Rubicon understands the crucial importance of privacy and confidentiality. We take legal obligations pertaining to data protection very seriously and ensure all information entrusted to us remains private and confidential.    





            Our Locations        


        We have an office in Dublin, located on Pearse Street and also in New York, based on 5th Avenue    





            Our Products        


        Rubicon is able to offer a comprehensive range of services across seven product lines. We pride ourselves in creating innovative products and solutions designed to maximise returns for clients. All our products are carefully crafted to meet the individual needs of our clients. We spend time getting to know our clients. It is only by doing so can we offer the right products and solutions to allow them fulfil their objectives.
We strive to exploit our experienced team's creativity and innovation in matching our products with each challenge a client presents. All our products are individually tailored, results driven and are executed with professionalism and integrity.    




