|Transportation





	The Rubicon team has vast experience in the transportation sector. The team has been involved in various market leading transactions which have consisted of a broad selection of assets including:


		Roads and Bridges

		Tunnels and Transit

		Rail and Light Rail

		Airports and Ports

		Parking and Rolling Stock


	The Rubicon team members have previously worked on some of the leading and most innovative transportation projects including:

	 
























				 
























	 













