Debt Procurement






Restructuring & Recapitalisation






Market Research & Direct Investment




|Capital Raising





Rubicon provides capital raising services. The firm can assist with creating shareholder value through raising third party equity to invest capital directly into infrastructure or energy companies, their existing asset portfolios or new investment platforms.

	Through our team's deep understanding of the global infrastructure sector and our extensive relationships with decision makers across all facets of the infrastructure industry, Rubicon can identify creative tactics and suitable partners to help raise active or passive capital to support growth.  This is often accomplished while maintaining the ownership and integrity of the company and its business. 













