Our team is vastly experienced in the transportation sector as evidenced by the wide range of transactions we have advised on, including roads, bridges, tunnels, transit, light rail, rail, airports, ports, parking and rolling stock. 














Rubicon team members have expertise in structuring renewable energy deals, including wind, solar, hydro, biomass, waste-to-energy and other renewable types. 














With specialised experience across the firm in conventional energy transactions, we offer a full range of advisory services to the energy industry, which encompasses generation, transmission and distribution facilities. 














Rubicon has a proven track record of providing advisory services on social projects that involve assets such as schools, universities, hospitals, courthouses, police stations, health clinics, laboratories, stadia, event venues, data centres, prisons and all forms of housing. 














Rubicon has the expertise to provide clients with services in the environmental sector which maximize returns and minimize risk. 








