|Mergers and Acquisitions





Rubicon provides Mergers and Acquisition services. The firm offers experienced knowledge and advice on the acquisition of infrastructure assets and/or companies.

	Given Rubicon’s extensive and diverse experience, we are ideally positioned to advise and assist investors on structuring and raising capital for acquisitions of large or medium-sized infrastructure or energy companies or assets. Members of Rubicon’s team have worked on some of the largest and most complex infrastructure M&A transactions to have closed over the past eight years.













